milestones.description: Vengsarkar has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 3110 runs, going past Gavaskar's 3092
John Wright has scored 18 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NZ breaking Martin Crowe's record
Azharuddin and Ajay Sharma's 127-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 113 between Kapil Dev and Ravi Shastri
This is the highest match aggregate (560) involving teams New Zealand & India in ODIs
